Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
