Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034,764)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.97,0:01:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这能找到海洋生物的最好标本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:06.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where can be found
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some of the finest specimens of undersea life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.15,0:01:11.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:11.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:15.01,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(520,952)}邮件
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.20,0:01:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一座奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An award?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没得过奖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never got an award before
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.25,0:01:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, rock
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.30,0:01:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an award
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小水母  我得奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish, I got an award
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.45,0:01:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小岛  我得奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.45,0:01:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Island, I got an awa--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须给海绵宝宝看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta show SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.15,0:01:41.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要动  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:41.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold still, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost done
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, guess what?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got an award
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么的奖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it for?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自己看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See for yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,颁发给杰出成就的成就
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For outstanding achievement in achievement--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,680)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这拼写我名字的方式好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:02.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a funny way to spell my name
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I think
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这奖杯应该是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the award is for me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定是误拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must have got it by mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.85,0:02:09.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这很闪亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:09.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's shiny
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.30,0:02:13.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你知道还有什么东西是闪亮的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:13.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you know what else is shiny?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.70,0:02:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找得到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can find it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这里头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别  那是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, don't, that's my--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装奖杯的壁橱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,award closet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要得奖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want an award
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't cry
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有一天你也会得奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll get an award one day
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.25,0:02:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不可能会得奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna get an award
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我什么事都没做成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I've never done anything
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你是派大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you're Patrick--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Star
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以想做什么就做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can do anything you want
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得倒轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's easy for you to say
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.47,0:02:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  要是你想要得奖的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, if you want to win an award
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须要做事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have to do something
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.40,0:03:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要打败巨猴人  拯救第九次元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to defeat the giant monkey man
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and save the ninth dimension
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.67,0:03:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过听起来有点小难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.67,0:03:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that sounds a little hard
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不先从小点的事情开始好不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't we start smaller?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.15,0:03:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要打败小猴人  拯救第八次元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna defeat the little monkey man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and save the eighth dimension
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smaller
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.95,0:03:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:12.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smaller
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.24,0:03:12.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消防员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:12.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fireman?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能想到最小的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The smallest you can think of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在蟹堡王上班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:17.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A job at the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上班期间时时刻刻做事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do things at work all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.70,0:03:27.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  蟹老板能让我上班人可真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:27.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, it was sure nice of Mr. Krabs to give me a job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:27.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,368)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且工资还是五十块一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And at $50 an hour, too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我开始在这上班的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I started working here
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得付蟹老板一百块一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had to pay Mr. Krabs $100 an hour
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.87,0:03:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猜猜谁入职了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess who just got a job?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猜猜谁离职了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess who just quit?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在得奖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I get my award yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须要努力争取才行  忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to work for it, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pick up order
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在得奖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:56.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I get my award now?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须把托盘带给顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:04:00.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have to take the tray to the customer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:05.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.97,0:04:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次要确保食物端到桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:09.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this time, make sure the food gets to the table
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.32,0:04:13.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:13.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是试点别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's try something different
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:21.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(736,236)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你只要接电话就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is answer the phone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是蟹堡王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  这是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, this is Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是蟹堡王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  这是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, this is Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是蟹堡王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不是蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not a Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那是这家餐厅的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that's the name of the restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,378)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fish paste
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三号桌那边积了点灰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks a little dusty around table three
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不你来打扫一下好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about if you sweep it out?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.87,0:04:58.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:58.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the point
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么事都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything right
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll do fine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么风把你从傻子镇吹来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just blow in from stupid town?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再接再厉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep trying, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.54,0:05:17.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有一堆给海绵宝宝的奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:17.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got a load of awards for SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凭什么我什么事都做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why can't I do anything right?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在是得不到奖的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna get an award now
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要放弃  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回我有件事你绝对可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This time I've got something I know you can do
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要开罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're gonna open a jar
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.22,0:05:43.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:43.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:45.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you try
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  拿罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, get a jar
