Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that's a pickle
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.12,0:05:49.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:49.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你需要罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need a jar
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.59,0:05:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试试这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try this
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在把盖子从罐子上拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, take the lid off the jar
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.90,0:06:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just relax
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抬起你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:03.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lift your hand
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.47,0:06:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把手放到盖子上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now put it on the lid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, the lid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.10,0:06:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.72,0:06:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lid
