Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lid--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.89,0:06:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freeze
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost there
