Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now head for the lid
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cold
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.63,0:06:25.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:25.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warmer
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.82,0:06:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warmer
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.98,0:06:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Warmer
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're hot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非常近了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on fire
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,近到烫死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:30.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It burns
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:31.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, OK
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.38,0:06:31.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:31.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着我的样子做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:34.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do exactly as I do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着我的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly as I do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.02,0:06:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.65,0:06:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照着你的样子做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly as you do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了  我弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I broke it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.03,0:06:53.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:53.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,触地得分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Touchdown
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是开罐大师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm jar master
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可太棒了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was great, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的已经掌握要领了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really got the hang of it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得我刚刚把手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember when I had my hand up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放到盖子上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I put it on the lid?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我把盖子拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then I took the lid off
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以为弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I thought I broke it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.95,0:07:19.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:19.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用手打开了罐子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I opened the jar with my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.45,0:07:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是因为你给我示范了怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it was all because you showed me how to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会忘记这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm never gonna forget this
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你就照着我的样子做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you do exactly what I do
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你迟早会得奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'll have an award in no time
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的好神奇能看到简单换件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how a simple change of clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让别人看起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can make a guy look--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just like me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要是想要赢得奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I'm gonna be an award-winner
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就必须穿得像个赢得奖杯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta dress like one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's creepy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过话说得挺好听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But flattering
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.46,0:08:00.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:00.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:03.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(426,432)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, back to the old grind
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.67,0:08:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, back to the old grind
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘戴帽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forgot my hat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锅铲掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dropped my spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在模仿我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're copying me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.90,0:09:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么要那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing that?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我就能得奖了  像你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I can win an award, like you
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's annoying
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.59,0:09:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就别这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, you're good
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.65,0:09:25.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:25.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.55,0:09:33.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玛丽有只小羊羔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:33.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mary had a little lamb
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它的绒毛白如
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,whose fleece was white as
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌椰菜鱼唇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pickled fish lips
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶海藻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seaweevil
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有鸡说鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yorgie shmorgies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我内心是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:48.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I'm safe inside my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.13,0:09:51.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我内心是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:51.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I'm safe inside my mind
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再模仿我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop copying me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样得不了奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no award for that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在大概可以进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's safe to go in now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你还要继续这样多久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, how long are you gonna keep this up?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直到我得的奖跟你一样多为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until I have as many awards as you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就走着瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No we won't
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.62,0:10:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是裤头村跳绳冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the jump rope champion of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:21.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我管这招叫切割跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call this one the slice and dice
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一条划痕都不留
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not a scratch on me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.87,0:10:38.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当我当得没意思了是吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:38.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not much fun being me now, huh, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.04,0:10:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我模仿你之前很早就开始做这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used to do this way before I started copying you
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:10:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望能让原本的派大星回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I had the old Patrick back
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他净是想要跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he just wants to be like me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  我是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Patrick Star
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.87,0:11:17.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是全裤头村最懒最粉的海星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:17.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the laziest, pinkest starfish in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.04,0:11:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好希望我是我自己  不是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I wish I were me, and not SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当个粉色的失败者有什么了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's so great about being a big pink loser?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我离得奖的距离就没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was never closer to an award
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比我开始学你的那一分钟还近过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than the minute I started copying you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.39,0:11:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's not here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奖杯快递
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trophy delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一个奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another trophy?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, great
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这回又是什么的奖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it for this time?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,颁发给什么事都不做的时间最久的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For doing absolutely nothing longer than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,794)}派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.83,0:11:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这奖杯是给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This trophy's for you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yay
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你现在要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what are you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要保住我的荣誉称号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go protect my title
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我是在开玩笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:06.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you thought I was kidding, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  在裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就连石头下都能发现优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,excellence can be found even under a rock
