Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每天都是海绵宝宝的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every day is a holiday for SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即使他要自己编一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,even if he has to make one up
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好  今天是莱弗埃里克松节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody, it's Leif Erikson Day
