Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是莱弗埃里克松节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Leif Erikson Day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.78,0:12:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有张字条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a note
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去找更多大纸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,went to get more giant paper
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.87,0:12:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,备注
