Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,莱弗埃里克松节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,happy Leif Erikson Day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶格亨得登革
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yerger hernder dernger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.30,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 模仿维京人口音，无实际意义 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So much for that
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能珊迪会来跟我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe Sandy will play with me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.88,0:13:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又一张字条
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another note
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去南方过冬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,went south for the winter
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱你的珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.17,0:13:07.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:07.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水温刚好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The water's fine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.99,0:13:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.73,0:13:16.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:16.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.15,0:13:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真希望能有个陪我玩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wish I had a buddy to play with
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接造一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll make one
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.23,0:13:24.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,木棍人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:24.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stick buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.55,0:13:26.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:26.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,石头人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rock buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.15,0:13:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水池人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sink buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.00,0:13:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,great
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,376)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要让你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for you to
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识认识章鱼哥跟蟹老板了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,meet Squidward and Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:08.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1152,198)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, come again
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我不上班的时候来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when I'm not working
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你还是要过来上班的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to enjoy your day off
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还怎么享受你的假期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you come to work anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想让你认识认识我的新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to meet my new friend
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这泡泡是你朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:14.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This bubble is your friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, he's handsome
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这点我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give him that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:22.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for stopping by
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还没接泡泡人的单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You haven't taken Bubble Buddy's order yet
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我凭什么要接
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是没有生命的物体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's an inanimate object
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的钱在这不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,his money's no good here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家的钱在这都管用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone's money is good here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在蟹堡王  我们会服务各式各样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At the Krusty Krab, we serves all kinds
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不帮泡泡接单
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking an order for a bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须接
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure you are
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,否则我就让你下半生吃不了兜着走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or I'll fill your life with misery and woe
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算你辞职也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even if you quit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能接你的单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I take your order?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来替你做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me decide for you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:15:03.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,188)}菜单
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双层堡堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Double Patty Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小小蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Junior Junior
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小乱堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:00.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jumble Small Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大三大四大二堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Junior Senior Sophomore Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双层夸脱盎司磅堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quarter Ouncer Double Pounder
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.51,0:15:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都好不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all so good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只要所有东西都来一份就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll just have one of everything
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有东西来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:09.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of everything?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,744)}泡泡人
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.79,0:15:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  带我们最好的顾客去餐桌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, show our best customer to his table
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡人渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:23.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Buddy's thirsty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.62,0:15:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来杯我们这最好的洗发露怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a glass of our finest shampoo
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.87,0:15:30.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sounds great
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,护发用品来了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your hair care product, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡人喜欢弯弯的吸管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.77,0:15:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Buddy likes bendy straws
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡人说味道很怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:47.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Buddy says it tastes funny
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.07,0:15:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,替顾客着想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:53.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think of the customer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silly me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你上成了无糖洗发露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:00.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got the diet shampoo
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:02.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有东西各一份给泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One of everything for Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡上面有奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's cheese on these patties
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.85,0:16:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡人乳糖不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Buddy's lactose intolerant
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可不能吃奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can't eat cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.05,0:16:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不然你就带着这些蟹黄堡再
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about you take these patties and sho--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.70,0:16:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:24.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥会再做一大盘的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward will make a fresh batch
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.15,0:16:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他也对面包过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he allergic to bread, too?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实他不喜欢面包皮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, he doesn't like the crust
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且章鱼哥  番茄酱应该在肉饼下面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Squidward, the ketchup should be under the patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且章鱼哥  腌椰菜应该放左边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Squidward, the pickles should be on the left side
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且章鱼哥  你应该
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Squidward, you should--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.69,0:16:47.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:47.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Squidward--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  所有东西各一份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, one of everything
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没奶酪  没面包皮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No cheese, no crust
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌椰菜放左边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pickles to the left
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.60,0:16:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四滴番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,four squirts of ketchup
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小麦面包  无乳生菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wheat buns, non-dairy lettuce
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人工饲养番茄  嘉年华样式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and farm-raised tomatoes, carnival style
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果还有别的事想要我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, if there's anything else I can do
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请  一定要犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,please, hesitate to ask
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱放桌上了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money's on the table, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  小子们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,餐饮行业就是服务至上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the restaurant game is all about service
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顾客永远是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The customer is always right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember that, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你总有一天会像我一样成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you'll be as successful as me one day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我学到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I learned my lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.40,0:17:28.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺带一提  泡泡人买单了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:28.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And by the way, Bubble Buddy picked up the tab
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble money
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码他们还留了小费
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least they left a tip
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了  泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are, Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goo Lagoon
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这有好多方式可以大玩特玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are lots of ways to have fun here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452,724)}欢迎来到酷乐湖
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  把我埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dudes, bury me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道我意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See what I mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.13,0:17:50.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,埋好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:50.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All done
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡人  你把他挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Buddy, you dig him out
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去买点棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I get some cotton candy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别光站那儿啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,潮快涨过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The tide's coming in
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.61,0:18:03.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:03.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:12.44,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(948,150)}港口公厕
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.55,0:18:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我朋友还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My friend's in there
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.64,0:18:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shake it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摇起来  对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shake it, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡屁股摇起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shake that bubble butt
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.77,0:18:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我屁股大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is my butt big?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是世界闻名的冲浪游民  邋遢石斑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.40,0:18:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the world famous surf bum, Grubby Grouper
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会见  石斑迷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Later, Groupies
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.40,0:18:42.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邋遢要去整点大家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:42.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grubby's gotta go catch some gnarly pounders
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.32,0:18:49.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会再洗这只鳍肢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:49.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never wash this flipper again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟泡泡人握个手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shake hands with Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他这是第一次自己上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's his first time on his own
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再次恭喜你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once again, congratulations
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆米花  花生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Popcorn, peanuts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:09.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,598)}此处需等待{\fnArial}45{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}分钟
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰镇冷饮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice cold drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:20.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,186)}港口公厕
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两小时够久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two hours is long enough
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你上完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:19.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're finished
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就让我们等一个泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He kept us waiting for a bubble?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说我们肥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He called us fat
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他洗了我的鳍肢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He washed my flipper
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他欠了我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He owes me money
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.35,0:19:41.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他让我提供了优质的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:41.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He made me provide excellent service
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  他让我经历了涨潮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dudes, he made me experience high tide
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.87,0:19:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他往我们供水系统里下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He poisoned our water supply
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烧了我们庄稼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,burned our crops
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把瘟疫带到了我们家里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and delivered a plague onto our houses
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.45,0:20:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可难道我们非得放任他等他这样做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But are we just gonna wait around until he does?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.25,0:20:05.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要推翻东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:05.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say we tip something over
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住救生员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get the lifeguard
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:17.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.43,0:20:20.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要对他施加这种无谓的暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:20.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't waste this senseless violence on him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是海绵宝宝的那个笨泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's that stupid bubble of SpongeBob's
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,导致了这一切的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's causing all the problems
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁挺我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们认识过我朋友泡泡人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you met my friend, Bubble Buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is, uh--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开了个针织小组吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of those sewing circles?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.17,0:20:45.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:45.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,介意不要把那些针离得那么近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:49.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you mind not getting so close with those pins?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尖锐物品会让泡泡人不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pointy objects make Bubble Buddy uncomfortable
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1076,918)}上厕所
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  那个泡泡必须消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, that bubble's gotta go
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他已经会上厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He already took care of that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.42,0:20:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是谢谢关心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But thanks for your concern
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.67,0:20:58.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消失成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:58.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go as an
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.12,0:21:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟那个泡泡就只会惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and that bubble have been nothing but trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to end it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.50,0:21:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会让你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们抓不到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:15.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never catch us now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.95,0:21:20.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:20.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ne--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ver
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闹够了吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough seahorsing around, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.35,0:21:28.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把泡泡给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give us that bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:31.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.49,0:21:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.49,0:21:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:33.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不止是个泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not just a bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是个泡泡人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's a Bubble Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是我的朋友  我爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's my friend and I love him
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就没有过很特别的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Haven't you ever had a very special friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.67,0:21:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,硬币人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nickel Buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.80,0:21:49.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没把你花掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:49.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never spend you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,古怪消音器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny Muffler
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉干兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jerky Pal
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.24,0:21:54.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钥匙布布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:54.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Booboo Keys
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,两个一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Snake Eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.47,0:21:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We love you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你们觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what do you say?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.67,0:22:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,扎破泡泡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pop the bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.64,0:22:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧把事解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好让我回家吹竖笛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can go home and play my clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.95,0:22:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.92,0:22:22.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:22.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.50,0:22:28.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:28.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.97,0:22:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我难道没发言权吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't I get a say in this?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.70,0:22:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改些时候见吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.67,0:22:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里的情况越来越怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Things are getting a little weird around here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,478)}出租车
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.77,0:22:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,莱弗埃里克松节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Leif Erikson Day
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是活的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's alive
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.00,0:22:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然他才讲不出这么好笑的笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Otherwise he couldn't tell such funny jokes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.04,0:22:59.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没意见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.04,0:22:59.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK by me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.84,0:23:00.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事成了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:00.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm done
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.79,0:23:01.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就好像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:01.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seems like
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.29,0:23:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今早还握着他的泡泡水瓶一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,only this morning I held his bottle
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.50,0:23:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小泡泡爆得好快
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They blow up so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.53,0:23:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
